27:31.331 --> 27:33.632
It's a rigorous, lengthy process.

27:34.312 --> 27:36.393
Some would say it's even jam-packed.

27:37.934 --> 27:42.375
But in the end, the finished product is well-developed and representative of the group, so it's very well worth it.

