potentially valid annual surveys and reliable surveys as a gift to LEAs and districts.

03:23:36.775 --> 03:23:37.676
That'd be wonderful.

03:23:37.716 --> 03:23:38.276
That'd be great.

03:23:38.376 --> 03:23:41.778
