09:12:30.963 --> 09:12:36.586
70% of California voters approved Prop 58 on November 8th of 2016.

09:12:36.726 --> 09:12:41.149
The amended statutes became effective July 1st of 2017.

09:12:42.130 --> 09:12:50.716
